ABOUT RAMADANBOT

RamadanBot is a faith-based platform designed to help Muslims deepen their
spiritual connection during Ramadan through personalized reflections and 
structured Qur'ānic reading guidance.

For more information, visit: https://www.ramadanbot.app

---

DUAL REPOSITORY STRUCTURE

This project is maintained using a dual repository setup:

1. PUBLIC REPOSITORY (ramadanbot-public)
   - Contains: README.md, LICENSE, Documentation
   - Purpose: Public documentation and guide
   - Visibility: Public on GitHub
   - URL: https://github.com/Abdallahnangere/ramadanbot-public

2. PRIVATE REPOSITORY (ramadanbot)
   - Contains: Full source code, API keys, configurations
   - Purpose: Development and deployment
   - Visibility: Private
   - Deployment: Automatic from main branch to Vercel

Third-party developers should refer to the public repository for guidelines
and documentation. The private repository is for authorized developers only.

